# FX Market Research agent — enables Claude-generated commentary + per-pair signals.
# Without it, live rates still load and signals fall back to a rule-based read.
# Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com → set the same var in Vercel project env.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# Enables LIVE data via Apify (calendar, news, retail sentiment):
#   - gochujang/economic-calendar-tracker (ForexFactory calendar, free)
#   - cloud9_ai/investing-news-scraper (Investing.com news, ~$0.002/headline)
#   - xtracto/myfxbook-community-outlook (Myfxbook retail % long/short, ~$0.02/pair)
# News grounds Claude's commentary; retail positioning adds a contrarian signal.
# Without the token, the calendar falls back to the curated list and commentary
# runs without news or sentiment.
# Get a token at https://console.apify.com/account/integrations
APIFY_TOKEN=apify_api_...
